name: Mackenzie Emerging Markets Bond Index ETF (CAD-Hedged)
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The Fund before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive EM USD Govt & Govt Related Bond Select CAD Hedged NTR Index or any successor thereto. It invests primarily in US dollar denominated, emerging market government bonds and governmentrelated bonds. Foreign currency exposure is hedged back to the Canadian dollar.
